channel.title: Hey! It's Raahul from Mumbai
channel.description:
Hello everyone,
I'm Raahul from Mumbai, India. I'm currently the Director of Engineering at a startup. Great to be part of this community! I hope to make a bigger impact in the world and this seems like the right place to learn more about that.
Cheers!
